<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA97">
<l>maṟaittulaka mēḻiṉilum vaittāyō vaṉṟē</l>
<l>luṟaippōṭu muṉkaik koṇṭāyō - niṟaittiṭ</l>
<l>ṭuḷainteḻuntu nīyerippa mūvulaku muḷpuk</l>
<l>kaḷainteḻunta centī yaḻal</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Do you keep it hidden inside the seven worlds, [or] if not,</l>
<l>do you hold it firmly in hand, when you, having filled [them]</l>
<l>rise destructively [and] burn [them], the red flaming fire</l>
<l>that rises entering the three worlds [and] mingling?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
